<fieldset>
<fieldset class="OrangeBorder">
<legend class="RedColor">MG_SKILLIXX_MULTIGAMES</legend>

This multigame map was made for the www.owlbox.de Community. It has a nice and different Design, a dark lightning and some good music. I don't had good ideas for unique Minigames. This map has 64 spawns. I used some MiP's and maps as minigames, thanks to the Authors that all are credited! If I missed someone write a comment.
</fieldset>

<fieldset>
<fieldset class="OrangeBorder">
<legend class="RedColor">MINIGAMES INSIDE</legend>

- Football
- Iceskate
- Smokebattle
- Aim 
- Knife
- Canyon Knife
- Grenade War
- Canon knife
- Skipping Rope
- AWP
- Dodgeball (with one ball and 10hp)
- Random (not even a game. LOL)
</fieldset>


<fieldset>
<fieldset class="OrangeBorder">
<legend class="RedColor">Last Words</legend>
Thanks to all guys that spend time on this map. Very big thanks to ColdZero that fixed Bugs for me and brought me to this effort. Thanks to robb for bringing me suggestions and other stuff! Thanks to [SG] Paul for letting me decompile a map of him to look at the way to prevent from knifing eachother.
And really thanks to all credited Mappers for their great maps and Stuff.
</fieldset>

<fieldset>
<fieldset class="OrangeBorder">
<legend class="RedColor">CHANGELOG</legend>
Fixed a bug in dodgeball where the ball could fly out of the field.
</fieldset>

<fieldset>
<fieldset class="OrangeBorder">
<legend class="RedColor">SONGLIST</legend>


- Starsplash - Cold as Ice
- Nelly - Hey Porsche
- DEV - Kiss my Lips
- Flo Rida - Wild ones
- Mint Royale - Singing in the rain
</fieldset>
